text: Haaksbergen is a municipality and town in the province of Overijssel, the Netherlands. About 24,000 people were living there in 2021. Haaksbergen lies in Twente region and borders both Achterhoek region and Germany. == References == * Plaatsengids.nl Category:Settlements in Overijssel Category:Municipalities of Overijssel Category:Twente
